<div id="modal_payroll_history" class="modal fade"><div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" style="width:88%"><div class="modal-content"><form id="form_payroll_history"><input type="hidden" name="id" id="ph_id"><div class="modal-header"><button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button><h4 class="modal-title" id="ph_modal_title">Create Payroll History Snapshot</h4></div><div class="modal-body"><div class="ph-hint"><strong>SAP hint:</strong> Payroll History sebaiknya menjadi arsip audit. Angka payroll diambil dari payroll result/payslip/posting, sedangkan edit hanya untuk status arsip, source, dan remarks.</div><div class="ph-section-title">Snapshot Source</div><div class="row"><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label class="required-label">Payroll Result Employee</label><select name="payroll_employee_id" id="payroll_employee_id" class="form-control"></select></div><div class="col-md-2 form-group"><label><?=hr_h('common_status', 'Status');?></label><select name="history_status" id="history_status" class="form-control"><option>ACTIVE</option><option>ARCHIVED</option><option>LOCKED</option><option>VOID</option></select></div><div class="col-md-3 form-group"><label>Audit Source</label><select name="audit_source" id="audit_source" class="form-control"><option>AUTO_SNAPSHOT</option><option>MANUAL_ADJUSTMENT</option><option>IMPORT</option></select></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-md-12 form-group"><label><?=hr_h('common_remarks', 'Remarks');?></label><textarea name="remarks" id="remarks" class="form-control" rows="3" placeholder="Catatan audit payroll history"></textarea></div></div></div><div class="modal-footer"><button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal"><?=hr_h('common_cancel', 'Cancel');?></button><button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa fa-save"></i> Save Snapshot</button></div></form></div></div></div>
